      <div xml:id="Sonnet41"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="happy"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
               <l>And there I saw the perfect bed.</l>
               <l> Just the perfect size, height width everything I could have dreamt.</l> 
               <l>I imagined the perfect sleep in my perfect bed.</l>
               <l>Never quite seeing home the same again.</l>
               <l>It came equipped with sheets and blankets even a heated mattress. </l>
               <l>This bed was better than anything I could have imagined.</l>
               <l>I climbed her leg and slipped myself in her pocket.</l>
               <l>I haven't slept this good in a long while</l>
